I managed to make it work for the backgroundColor (square part of the shape below), but not for the ellipse.

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/44491123/190258674-a22298e7-9f7e-4915-b0c8-4d0b7c866881.png)

I have setup the following property on this component:

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/44491123/190259706-cfa5fd5b-c147-4491-8a9d-78cfac861f4d.png)

This results in the following generated code:
```ts
import React from "react";
import { getOverrideProps } from "@aws-amplify/ui-react/internal";
import { Icon } from "@aws-amplify/ui-react";
export default function Ellipse26(props) {
  const { color = "#CD7F32", overrides, ...rest } = props;
