![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/44491123/190261208-eb4c7da1-dceb-49a7-9a4a-25ca55c57490.png)

Is there a way to set up that component so that I can change its color via a property, as I do no want to change the `paths` property entirely?

Any help appriciated.

